## Auth

The Arcade Figma MCP Server uses the [Figma auth provider](/references/auth-providers/figma) to connect to users' Figma accounts.

With the Arcade Cloud Platform, there's nothing to configure. Your users will see `Arcade` as the name of the application that's requesting permission.

With a self-hosted installation of Arcade, you need to [configure the Figma auth provider](/references/auth-providers/figma#configuring-figma-auth) with your own Figma app credentials.

